## 2. Duplicate `_getInitials` Helper

The exact same initials-extraction logic is duplicated as a **private method** in **7+ files**:

| File | Method Signature |
|---|---|
| [category_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/categories/category_list_screen.dart) | *(uses inline)* |
| [category_edit_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/categories/category_edit_screen.dart#L386-L394) | `_getInitials(String name)` |
| [doctors_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/doctors/doctors_list_screen.dart#L399-L405) | `_getInitials(String?, String?)` |
| [diagnosis_types_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/diagnosis_types/diagnosis_types_list_screen.dart#L354-L362) | `_getInitials(String name)` |
| [diagnosis_type_edit_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/diagnosis_types/diagnosis_type_edit_screen.dart#L403-L409) | `_getInitials(String? name)` |
| [franchise_labs_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/franchise_labs/franchise_labs_list_screen.dart#L440-L453) | `_getInitials(String? name)` |
| [franchise_edit_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/franchise_labs/franchise_edit_screen.dart#L432-L442) | `_getInitials(String? name)` |
| [user_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/profile/user_list_screen.dart#L409-L415) | `_getInitials(String?, String?)` |

**What's wrong:** Two different signatures exist (`single name` vs `firstName + lastName`), but the core logic is identical. Any bug fix must be applied 7+ times.

**Recommendation:** Create a single top-level utility:
```dart
// lib/methods/string_utils.dart
String getInitials(String? firstName, [String? lastName]) { ... }
```

