## 6. Duplicate `_buildErrorWidget`

Inline error placeholder appears in **3+ edit screens** with different styling each time:

| File | Style |
|---|---|
| doctor_edit_screen.dart | Simple `Text` with error color |
| diagnosis_type_edit_screen.dart | Simple `Text` with padding |
| franchise_edit_screen.dart | Full `TintedContainer` with icon + retry button (~60 lines) |

**What's wrong:** Inconsistent error UX. Franchise screen has a rich retry widget; others show plain text.

**Recommendation:** Standardize into a single `InlineErrorWidget` that always supports a retry callback.

