## 8. Duplicate Details-Card Section Header

Every edit screen has an identical "section header" inside the details card — an icon container + title text inside a tinted row:

| File | Pattern |
|---|---|
| category_edit_screen.dart L224–L253 | `Container > Row > [icon-box, title]` |
| doctor_edit_screen.dart L433–L466 | identical |
| diagnosis_type_edit_screen.dart L265–L291 | identical |
| franchise_edit_screen.dart L265–L297 | identical |

**Recommendation:** Extract to a `SectionHeader` widget:
```dart
class SectionHeader extends StatelessWidget {
  final IconData icon;
  final String title;
  final Color color;
}
```

