## 9. Duplicate List-Screen Scaffold

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The **5 list screens** follow an identical structural pattern that could be abstracted.

All of these screens share this **exact same structure**:
1. `WindowScaffold` with `CenterSearchBar` + `FloatingActionButton`
2. `asyncProvider.when(data → filter → grid/empty, loading → skeleton grid, error → buildErrorState)`
3. Grid with `TintedContainer` + `AppInkWell` cards
4. Private `_filter*`, `getCrossAxisCount`, `getChildAspectRatio`, `_buildLoadingState`, `_buildSkeletonLoader`, `_buildErrorState`, `_buildEmptyState` methods

| File | Lines | Entity |
|---|---|---|
| [category_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/categories/category_list_screen.dart) | 385 | Categories |
| [doctors_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/doctors/doctors_list_screen.dart) | 407 | Doctors |
| [diagnosis_types_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/diagnosis_types/diagnosis_types_list_screen.dart) | 364 | Diagnosis Types |
| [franchise_labs_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/franchise_labs/franchise_labs_list_screen.dart) | 455 | Franchise Labs |
| [user_list_screen.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/profile/user_list_screen.dart) | 417 | Users |

**Total duplicated lines:** ~2,028 lines doing essentially the same thing.

**Recommendation:** Create a generic `EntityListScreen<T>` widget that accepts:
- Provider, filter function, card builder, FAB label, empty/error messages
- Or at minimum, extract `getCrossAxisCount`, `getChildAspectRatio`, and `_buildLoadingState` into shared helpers.

