## 10. Duplicate Skeleton / Shimmer Loader

Every list screen has its own `_buildSkeletonLoader` with slightly different layouts but the same core pattern (CircleAvatar + rectangular placeholders):

| File | Variant |
|---|---|
| category_list_screen.dart | Column-based |
| doctors_list_screen.dart | Row-based |
| diagnosis_types_list_screen.dart | Row-based (identical to doctors) |
| franchise_labs_list_screen.dart | Row-based (identical to doctors) |
| user_list_screen.dart | Row-based |

**Recommendation:** Create a `SkeletonCardLoader` widget with a `variant` parameter (`row` or `column`).

