## 11. Duplicate Responsive Grid Helpers

`getCrossAxisCount()` and `getChildAspectRatio()` are **identical** (or near-identical) across all 5 list screens:

```dart
// Identical in all 5 screens
int getCrossAxisCount(BuildContext context) {
  final size = MediaQuery.of(context).size;
  if (size.width < initialWindowWidth && size.width > 1200) return 3;
  if (size.width < 1200) return 2;
  return 4;
}
```

**Recommendation:** Move to a shared utility:
```dart
// lib/methods/responsive_helpers.dart
int getResponsiveCrossAxisCount(BuildContext context) { ... }
double getResponsiveAspectRatio(BuildContext context, {double base = 2.3}) { ... }
```

