## 13. Two Competing TextField Widgets

| Widget | File | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `CustomTextField` | [custom_text_field.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/ui_components/custom_text_field.dart) | Used **everywhere** |
| `ReusableTextField` | [reusable_ui_components.dart](file:///home/himanshu/Documents/Repositories/LabLedger/lib/screens/ui_components/reusable_ui_components.dart#L1-L146) | Lines 1–146 — **appears unused** |

**What's wrong:** `ReusableTextField` has a different API (different border radius `16` vs `12`, different fill color logic, different label/hint handling). Having two text field widgets creates confusion and inconsistency.

**Recommendation:** Audit usage. If `ReusableTextField` is truly unused, **delete it**. If it's used somewhere, consolidate into `CustomTextField`.

