### Recommended Action Order
1. **Immediate** (zero risk): Items 15, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 11
2. **Short-term** (low risk, high reward): Items 7, 8, 12, 6, 10
3. **Planned refactor** (medium effort): Items 9, 13, 14

> [!TIP]
> Items 1–6 and 11 are **pure extraction refactors** — no UI change at all, just moving private methods to shared utilities. Items 7–10 and 12 involve creating new reusable widgets that replace inline code, which requires more careful testing.
